:0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:08:03.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 譴責<br />\n咪同口交部強烈譴責一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b9eb596ae2c68d775b1fc041c8ade1d1c10a3b","tid":392042,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:08:15.000Z","msg":"基本法第27條保障言論自由<br />\n<br />\n《基本法》第二十七條規定，香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由。據了解，聯署的醫生諮詢法律意見後，認為醫委會專業守則限制醫生自我宣傳的條文，可能違反上述《基本法》保障港人的權利，並可能牴觸人權法，<span style=\"color: red;\">法律意見又指言論自由應只在涉及誹謗、危害國家安全或社會秩序時才受限制</span>，醫生宣揚個人資料應不受此限。&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20051007/5289906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20051007%2F5289906&d=QPMYM8xAWUTO%2B%2B3pTDZb0o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=fdfe6d8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20051007%2F5289906&h=1b0f48f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20051007/5289906</a><br />\n<br />\n等睇釋法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f30f3dbafa79c2b977ecb858669b5651808a46","tid":392042,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:12:04.000Z","msg":"Cctvb係咪del左post"},{"pid":"4bd67e2cd8223b3f702a9d8ff06ea68ca740f7ca","tid":392042,"uid":56559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:13:37.000Z","msg":"靠嚇啊<br />\n犯邊條法？"},{"pid":"803fc26c894586aad1c15d4a53bf3f3ce5a8684b","tid":392042,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:15:56.000Z","msg":"有咩限制？<br />\n恭喜人犯左乜法？"},{"pid":"fd78493610c20f70836b01b45aa908f537c9372d","tid":392042,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:18:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以後會唔會屌你老母都唔撚講得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></