,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:57:19.000Z","msg":"行動升級，夾錢報紙頭板啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a115a3ab0ca9e6c083b25673559dc7377f4d0fb","tid":392042,"uid":92736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:59:19.000Z","msg":"有限制自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0d64c385584cfbd5a6f24d6b2bc4ec8f69fb19","tid":392042,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:00:11.000Z","msg":"你咪拉佢坐監囉，咁大不滿"},{"pid":"79489f19dfa5ff8438d43771e91bbd016638d1a1","tid":392042,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:05:57.000Z","msg":"林鄭聲明原文：<br />\n<br />\n特首譴責校園不當言論<br />\n2017年09月08日<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥表示，昨天驚悉有人在香港教育大學校園學生告示板（「民主牆」）上張貼對剛經歷喪子傷痛的教育局副局長極之涼薄和侮辱的字句，她感到極度遺憾，並予以強烈譴責。<br />\n <br />\n她說，對於在大專院校出現這種完全不尊重他人感受、有違道德的冷血言論，社會整體都表示震驚和悲憤。她昨晚已聯絡教育大學校長張仁良，表達對事件極度關注。<br />\n <br />\n她又說，留意到最近不同大學校園均有人張貼主張「港獨」的標語。「港獨」不符合「一國兩制」、《基本法》以及香港社會的整體和長遠利益。對於大學校園持續出現此等違背國家主權、領土完整和發展利益的言論，她亦予以譴責。<br />\n <br />\n林鄭月娥強調，言論自由並非完全沒有限制，而學術自由和院校自主也非鼓吹歪論的藉口。上述言論已超越社會底線，大眾對此定有公論。<br />\n <br />\n她期望校方盡快採取適當行動處理，也期望各界合力糾正這種濫用言論自由的行為，維持公民社會的核心價值，共同捍衞社會應有的道德標準。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/tc/categories/admin/html/2017/09/20170908_164306.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcategories%2Fadmin%2Fhtml%2F2017%2F09%2F20170908_164306.shtml&d=QPMYM8xAWUTO%2B%2B3pTDZb0o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=77f2a717\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/tc/categories/admin/html/2017/09/20170908_164306.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"fbea36b11769045390b5c26e5e718ffab73a4568","tid":392042,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:07:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下個到林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢仆街仲開心"},{"pid":"3505f5ab92e77be51b9def9a7b5bd2eceaa2fc91","tid":392042,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:08:03.000Z","msg":"有限制都係自由中國咪好自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5e5895c81dd1dd71059d5c0c262bccb1802c7a","tid":392042,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:18:17.000Z","msg":"受到上帝感召慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9729a2dbbe0ea26109ebfc27e65479b7b98b0b","tid":392042,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:25:57.000Z","msg":"咁鵝頸橋個班阿婆係咪要拉晒去坐監？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c35dbb900aa1ef29e16e8fa3da550eba210719","tid":392042,"uid":114547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:27:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩限制 犯左法呀？駛唔駛坐監呀？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能要嫁，修改基本法再告你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />現今政府就係咁玩，有時政府柒左既話多數會講個別事件不作評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96a5cc7a50bf2daf36e8ace34a79fc4a4403114","tid":392042,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:47:07.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 咁寺廟班神棍應該第一班比人批鬥"},{"pid":"8a57e4ea285897909a7f65fa6eb44a419f83d6ca","tid":392042,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:48:33.000Z","msg":"人人有份永不落空 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c91a758ef3810db225751e0dfa43437b052d6e","tid":392042,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:53:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行動升級，夾錢報紙頭板啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/no